data.description: One of the most beautiful streets in the city!  Small town life across from districted Middle and High Schools.  This updated all-brick home is a must see!  Beautiful kitchen and new floors throughout most of the home.  One level living with fenced in backyard.  Updates include Kitchen 2022, Roof 2022, Windows 2012, Floors 2021.  Detached 1 car garage with new garage door and motor.  Minutes from High Point Rockers Baseball stadium, High Point Regional Hospital, High Points new social district, Public Library, and Saturdays open air farmers market.  Schedule your appointment to see this one!
